txt.en: 'Did you really think you could win?'
'I will show the giants the worth of our alliance!'
'You should have run when you had the chance!'
'Only a fool would stand against our combined might.'
'I will bury you all in the frost and snow!'
'You will not leave this mountain alive!'
'All this effort for an egg? Noble, but foolish.'
'Giants! Hit the [placeholder] [placeholder] with a rock! That is how to win the game.'
